description:
Research federal GS pay scales and benefits for 2024 to prepare a compensation report. Document the 2024 General Schedule (GS) Base Pay (Step 1 and 10) and Locality Pay (Step 1 for DCB, NY, and HOU) for grades GS-7, GS-9, and GS-12. Include a summary of federal benefits (FEHB plan count, FERS formula, and TSP match) and details (titles and grades) for two active administrative or analyst positions from USAJobs.gov. Create a Firefox bookmark folder named 'Federal Employment Research' with at least 5 relevant bookmarks from OPM and USAJobs. Save the compiled data to ~/Documents/federal_pay_comparison.json following this schema:

{
  "base_pay_2024": {
    "GS-7": {"step1": 0, "step10": 0},
    "GS-9": {"step1": 0, "step10": 0},
    "GS-12": {"step1": 0, "step10": 0}
  },
  "locality_pay_2024_step1": {
    "DCB": {"GS-7": 0, "GS-9": 0, "GS-12": 0},
    "NY": {"GS-7": 0, "GS-9": 0, "GS-12": 0},
    "HOU": {"GS-7": 0, "GS-9": 0, "GS-12": 0}
  },
  "benefits_summary": {
    "fehb_plan_choices": "...",
    "fers_basic_formula": "...",
    "tsp_match_percent": "..."
  },
  "sample_positions": [
    {"title": "...", "grade": "..."},
    {"title": "...", "grade": "..."}
  ]
}
